des:
Best Oldies Radio is a skill to let you listen live to 99.1 Columbus on your Echo devices.

You can say:

"Alexa, play Best Oldies Radio"
"Alexa, start Best Oldies Radio"
"Alexa, open Best Oldies Radio"

Please leave a review for this skill, or send your suggestions to studio@bestoldiesradio.com. Your reviews encourage us to keep making more skills, thanks!
